Another task you are responsible for the the budget for the coming years.
Their are 4 categories that funds can be placed. The first is the staff 
budget which will help keep mistakes from happening in the plant and will
have positive effects in productivity of the plant. The Investment budget
that is used to research better energy production methods and transportation.
Public relations is also a huge key factor in many power plants and your
plant is no exception, without a proper PR team your plant may go under to
competitive power plants. Finally their is the basic plant maintenance budget
that is used to keep the plant itself safe and power efficient.
